      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines a comprehensive, full-stack web platform for Zain Tech, focusing on a public website, user authentication, a user dashboard, an LMS, a booking system, and administrative panels. Due to the complexity and the lack of suitable Wix Apps provided, the plan will leverage Wix CMS for content management and structure, acknowledging that a full-stack application of this scope requires custom backend development beyond the capabilities of Wix CMS alone."
